{"tid":1530132,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"支共恐嚇手法：不停口交","createTime":"2019-09-02T01:20:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T01:32:34.000Z","uid":52230,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a0e73989a76fbc8e3e3ba0aaf9facfa899246075","tid":1530132,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:20:58.000Z","msg":"例一： <br />\n口交：若香港不能自行平息，中共可派出摺被軍平亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笠水：中央相信香港有能力平息<br />\n目的：大鳩你咪撚再搞亂檔<br />\n傻鳩藍絲：党好強硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對暴徒好寬容<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事實：摺被軍一出比美帝制裁到屎忽窿都不保<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例二：<br />\n口交：星期六港府可出緊急法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笠水：環時總編黎做公關show：香港局勢緩和，不必緊急法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n目的：中央大把計搞鳩你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傻鳩藍絲：緊急法一出，拉鳩晒暴徒，党好強大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事實：港共冇權做，出左外資都走晒，支共個癩痢頭又癩多撻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔驚你就唔洗咁多口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總結：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sGaLSuD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsGaLSuD.jpg&h=292b693c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"868956ac90a147b8529e7beac0c09ffec10c0793","tid":1530132,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:22:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83eb07e0472ec8fd459dd03444db9686afcffec8","tid":1530132,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:22:58.000Z","msg":"屌唔撚識郁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc366181cedb8cb5d8bb1fc52f851d88d38f3b76","tid":1530132,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"868956ac90